OL,3,C'Why was this allowed to happen?':
OL,4,CSouthport mum demands answers
OL,6,FThe mother of a young girl caught up
OL,7,Fin the Southport attack has asked "how
OL,8,Fmany more lives will be destroyed
OL,9,Fbefore the system takes
OL,10,Fresponsibility?"
OL,12,FSpeaking at the public inquiry into
OL,13,Fthe attack, the mum of the girl, known
OL,14,Fonly as Child M, urged it to "tell us
OL,15,Fhow we ever got to this point, why was
OL,16,Fthis allowed to happen. Why was no
OL,17,Faction taken?"
