OL,3,C'Why was this allowed to happen?':
OL,4,CSouthport mum demands answers
OL,6,FReading her impact statement, the mum
OL,7,Frecounted how she went into the
OL,8,Fbuilding frantically trying to find
OL,9,Fher daughter.
OL,11,FThe woman, who was accompanied by her
OL,12,Fhusband to read her impact statement,
OL,13,Fdescribed seeing children lying on the
OL,14,Ffloor and blood along the walls when
OL,15,Fshe arrived to pick her daughter up
OL,16,Ffrom the dance class.
