OL,3,C'Why was this allowed to happen?':
OL,4,CSouthport mum demands answers
OL,6,FShe said: "I will not describe what I
OL,7,Fsaw when I went up the stairs or into
OL,8,Fthe studio, other than seeing the
OL,9,Fcoward lying face down on the floor
OL,10,Fbeing arrested.
OL,12,F"But that scene is burnt into my
OL,13,Fmemory and is a continual companion.
OL,14,FIt haunts me appearing both in my
OL,15,Fnightmares and during the frequent
OL,16,Fflashbacks I continue to experience
OL,17,Fdaily."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
