OL,3,C'Why was this allowed to happen?':
OL,4,CSouthport mum demands answers
OL,6,FShe found her daughter safe at a
OL,7,Fnearby house where "physically she was
OL,8,Funharmed, but the damage was already
OL,9,Fdone."
OL,11,FThe mother said that the family had
OL,12,Fbeen unable to throw away the trainers
OL,13,Fthat their child had been wearing,
OL,14,Fadding: "We will now forever keep what
OL,15,Fto others look like old, battered
OL,16,Ftrainers.
OL,18,F"Because they aren't just old,
OL,19,Fbattered trainers; they were on her
OL,20,Ffeet when she had to run for her life."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
