OL,3,C'Why was this allowed to happen?':
OL,4,CSouthport mum demands answers
OL,6,FShe said she wanted the inquiry to
OL,7,Ftell them: "Why was this allowed to
OL,8,Fhappen".
OL,10,FShe continued: "Why was no action
OL,11,Ftaken? What change is coming, not in
OL,12,Ftheory but in practice?
OL,14,F"How many more lives will be destroyed
OL,15,Fbefore the system takes responsibility?
OL,17,F"This Inquiry is the chance, maybe the
OL,18,Fonly chance, to demand real answers,
OL,19,Fto expose every failing and to force
OL,20,Fmeaningful and lasting change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
