OL,3,C'Why was this allowed to happen?':
OL,4,CSouthport mum demands answers
OL,6,F"You must take this chance, you must
OL,7,Fbe the change.
OL,9,FShe added: "To the girls who survived,
OL,10,Fyou are so brave. You are true heroes.
OL,12,F"To the parents of Elsie, Bebe and
OL,13,FAlice, there is not an hour that goes
OL,14,Fby where I don't think of all of you.
OL,15,FI am in awe of the wonderful
OL,16,Fcommunities you are creating in memory
OL,17,Fof your beautiful girls.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
